{"tid":352943,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"各位巴絲入黎睇下 幫幫忙救下呢隻狗仔","createTime":"2017-08-09T07:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T16:17:08.000Z","uid":81793,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"13acfaaf0ce7300ea23005cba138c6ab00d0daec","tid":352943,"uid":81793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T07:29:48.000Z","msg":"佢身世好可憐 難得搵到好主人<br />\n好日子只係過左唔係好耐咋<br />\n點解個天又要咁對佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相信有養寵物嘅各位<br />\n絕對明白主人有幾需要大家幫忙<br />\n就算未必能夠捐款幫手<br />\n都希望大家都可以share出去等多d人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/152706_ead3bcca385f8745e1393cf45cc28b8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F152706_ead3bcca385f8745e1393cf45cc28b8d.jpg&h=c445ba69&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/152709_2b7a92770b7638f10d9a2ad3881b499d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F152709_2b7a92770b7638f10d9a2ad3881b499d.jpg&h=6c74de66&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/152712_6ef2378af0e1e35da9cd768be41c67d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F152712_6ef2378af0e1e35da9cd768be41c67d5.jpg&h=55e340aa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/152714_c49fbbe5046ed89a8fa9c77c933f4ab7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F152714_c49fbbe5046ed89a8fa9c77c933f4ab7.jpg&h=a249a856&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：並非主人 希望有更多好心人救下狗仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.g